  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead yourself to victory in your own tank. You thought that you need the entire crew to drive such a vehicle? Then you were right.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But not in this game! You have to switch between seats inside the tank in order to win. It is not a super realistic simulator but a casual game based on historical equipment. Put your multitasking to the test by trying to complete the tasks of up to 5 crew members just by yourself. Simultaneously drive, navigate, aim, load and look around - and most importantly - survive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>There is also a two-player co-op mode.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Choose ammunition!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139290/extras/3cc8de98255c57e3452e948af2631465.poster.avif?t=1770915214\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139290/extras/3cc8de98255c57e3452e948af2631465.webm?t=1770915214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139290/extras/3cc8de98255c57e3452e948af2631465.mp4?t=1770915214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Blow up your opponents!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139290/extras/9486811246fa6de12ff5948130524adc.poster.avif?t=1770915214\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139290/extras/9486811246fa6de12ff5948130524adc.webm?t=1770915214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139290/extras/9486811246fa6de12ff5948130524adc.mp4?t=1770915214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achieve victory in four different tanks on dedicated maps:</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Sd. Kfz. 222</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3 crew members</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 20mm main cannon with a magazine</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > coaxial machine gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > four wheeler</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>T-34-85</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5 crew members</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > main gun 85mm</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > coaxial machine gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > bow machine gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > armour-piercing and high explosive ammunition</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>M4A2 (76) W HVSS</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5 crew members</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > main 76mm gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > coaxial machine gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > bow machine gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > armour-piercing and high explosive ammunition</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Tiger I</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5 crew members</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > main 88mm gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > coaxial machine gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > bow machine gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > armour-piercing and high explosive ammunition</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead yourself to victory in your own tank. You thought that you need the entire crew to drive such a vehicle? Then you were right.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But not in this game! You have to switch between seats inside the tank in order to win. It is not a super realistic simulator but a casual game based on historical equipment. Put your multitasking to the test by trying to complete the tasks of up to 5 crew members just by yourself. Simultaneously drive, navigate, aim, load and look around - and most importantly - survive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>There is also a two-player co-op mode.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Choose ammunition!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139290/extras/3cc8de98255c57e3452e948af2631465.poster.avif?t=1770915214\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139290/extras/3cc8de98255c57e3452e948af2631465.webm?t=1770915214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139290/extras/3cc8de98255c57e3452e948af2631465.mp4?t=1770915214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Blow up your opponents!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139290/extras/9486811246fa6de12ff5948130524adc.poster.avif?t=1770915214\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139290/extras/9486811246fa6de12ff5948130524adc.webm?t=1770915214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2139290/extras/9486811246fa6de12ff5948130524adc.mp4?t=1770915214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achieve victory in four different tanks on dedicated maps:</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Sd. Kfz. 222</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 3 crew members</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 20mm main cannon with a magazine</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > coaxial machine gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > four wheeler</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>T-34-85</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5 crew members</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > main gun 85mm</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > coaxial machine gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > bow machine gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > armour-piercing and high explosive ammunition</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>M4A2 (76) W HVSS</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5 crew members</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > main 76mm gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > coaxial machine gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > bow machine gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > armour-piercing and high explosive ammunition</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Tiger I</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5 crew members</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > main 88mm gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > coaxial machine gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > bow machine gun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > armour-piercing and high explosive ammunition</p></li></ul>",
